        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Key Insights\n",
        "\n",
        "### Summary of Bond Pricing Results\n",
        "\n",
        "1. **Maturity Effect**: Bond prices decrease with maturity (more discounting)\n",
        "2. **Rate Effect**: Higher initial rates → Lower bond prices\n",
        "3. **Volatility Effect**: Higher volatility → Higher bond prices (convexity option value)\n",
        "4. **Estimation Accuracy**: Standard errors are small (~0.01%) with 5000 paths\n",
        "\n",
        "### Next Steps\n",
